"title": "1690: word of God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1690: word of god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The utterances of God, especially as revealed in Scripture. This may take the form of commands or promises. The term can also refer to Jesus Christ as the incarnate Word of God.</p>\n<h2>The word of God revealed as law</h2>\n<h3>God has made his commands and requirements known</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:19\">PSA 147:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:1-Exod20:17\">EXO 20:1–20:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:3\">EXO 24:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:27-Exod34:28\">EXO 34:27–34:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:5\">DEU 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:3\">ISA 2:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:2\">MIC 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:6\">MAT 15:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:13\">MRK 7:13</a></p>\n<h3>God's law is to be obeyed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:14\">DEU 30:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:6\">JOS 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:4\">PSA 119:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:21\">LUK 8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:28\">LUK 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22-Jas1:23\">JAS 1:22–1:23</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of disobedience and its consequences</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:31\">NUM 15:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:23-1Sam15:26\">1SA 15:23–15:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:9\">2SA 12:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:13\">1CH 10:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:21\">2CH 34:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:24\">ISA 5:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:9\">JER 8:9</a></p>\n<h2>The word of God as prophecy</h2>\n<h3>The prophets spoke the words of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:9\">JER 1:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:1\">1SA 3:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:3\">JER 25:3</a></strong> <em>God's prophetic word came to Israel with varying frequency.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:24\">1KI 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:2\">2KI 24:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:12\">2CH 36:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15\">2CH 36:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:13\">ISA 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:3\">ISA 24:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:1\">JER 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:1\">JER 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:11-Amos8:12\">AMO 8:11–8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:1\">MAL 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Prophetic introductory formulae</h3>\n<p>``The word of the LORD came to ...'':\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1\">GEN 15:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:10\">1SA 15:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:11\">2SA 24:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:11\">1KI 6:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:4\">2KI 20:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:4\">ISA 38:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:1\">JER 16:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:1\">EZK 6:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:1\">JON 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:1\">ZEC 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:19\">1KI 22:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:16\">2KI 20:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:5\">ISA 39:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:10\">ISA 1:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:4\">JER 2:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:1\">HOS 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:5\">2SA 7:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:4\">1CH 17:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:6\">2KI 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:6\">ISA 37:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:5\">JER 2:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:4\">EZK 2:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3\">AMO 1:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:11\">HAG 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>Prophetic predictions fulfilled</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:15\">1KI 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:29\">1KI 15:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:12\">1KI 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:34\">1KI 16:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:38\">1KI 22:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:17\">2KI 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:36\">2KI 9:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:17\">2KI 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:25\">2KI 14:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:12\">2KI 15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:16\">2KI 23:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:21-2Chr36:22\">2CH 36:21–36:22</a></p>\n<h3>The word ``against'' a people, indicating judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:8\">ISA 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:22\">ISA 37:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:30\">JER 25:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:1\">AMO 3:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:5\">ZEP 2:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:1\">ZEC 9:1</a></p>\n<h3>True prophecy is inspired by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:20-2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:20–1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:16\">JER 23:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:25-Jer23:26\">JER 23:25–23:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:30\">JER 23:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:1-Ezek13:3\">EZK 13:1–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>A true prophet hears from God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:12\">2KI 3:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:13\">JER 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:18\">JER 23:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:18\">JER 27:18</a></p>\n<h3>The prophetic word is to be heeded</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:20-Exod9:21\">EXO 9:20–9:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:10\">JER 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:3\">JER 25:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a></p>\n<h2>The word of God as Scripture</h2>\n<h3>Scripture is the written word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:2\">DAN 9:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:2\">ROM 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a></p>\n<h3>NT writings are classified as Scripture</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:16\">2PE 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Scripture is inspired and true</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:35\">JHN 10:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>The foundational importance of Scripture</h3>\n<p>It must not be distorted or changed:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:2\">DEU 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:32\">DEU 12:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:6\">PRO 30:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:2\">2CO 4:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:15\">2TI 2:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:19\">REV 22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:1-Neh8:8\">NEH 8:1–8:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:13\">1TI 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:2\">PSA 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:15\">PSA 119:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:97\">PSA 119:97</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:20\">ISA 8:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:11\">ACT 17:11</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:29\">MAT 22:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:24\">MRK 12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:2\">ACT 17:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:28\">ACT 18:28</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:6\">1CO 4:6</a> <em>It sets the limit of authoritative doctrine.</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as the incarnate Word of God</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is God in the flesh</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1\">JHN 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:45\">JHN 12:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">HEB 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1\">1JN 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:13\">REV 19:13</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ speaks the Father's words</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:40\">JHN 8:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:16\">MAT 22:16</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:14\">MRK 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:21\">LUK 20:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:18\">JHN 7:18</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's words have sovereign power</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:8\">MAT 8:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:7\">LUK 7:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:16\">MAT 8:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>The gospel as the word of God</h2>\n<h3>It was preached by Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:2\">MRK 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:19-Matt13:23\">MAT 13:19–13:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:14-Mark4:20\">MRK 4:14–4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:11-Luke8:15\">LUK 8:11–8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:33\">MRK 4:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:38\">MRK 1:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:1\">LUK 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>It was preached by the first Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">1TH 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:20\">MRK 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:2\">ACT 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4\">ACT 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:1\">ACT 11:1</a> <em>to the Gentiles</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:5\">ACT 13:5</a> <em>to the Jews</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:35-Acts15:36\">ACT 15:35–15:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:13\">ACT 17:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:36\">1CO 14:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:2\">2CO 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:14\">PHP 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:25\">COL 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to numerical and spiritual growth within the church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:7\">ACT 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:24\">ACT 12:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:49\">ACT 13:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:20\">ACT 19:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:5-Col1:6\">COL 1:5–1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">1TH 2:13</a> <em>Paul stresses that the preached word is not merely a verbal message but a dynamic power which achieves things.</em></p>\n<h3>It must be preached</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:14\">ROM 10:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Descriptions of God's word</h2>\n<p>It is true:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:4\">PSA 33:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:17\">JHN 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:31\">2SA 22:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30\">PSA 18:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:5\">PRO 30:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:10\">2KI 10:10</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:20\">PSA 103:20</a> <em>It is obeyed by angels.</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:89\">PSA 119:89</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:152\">PSA 119:152</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:8\">ISA 40:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:25\">1PE 1:25</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:103\">PSA 119:103</a> <em>It is sweet and delightful</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:2\">PSA 138:2</a> <em>It is exalted above all things</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:23\">ISA 45:23</a> <em>It is irrevocable</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:17\">EPH 6:17</a> <em>It is the sword of the Spirit</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:9\">2TI 2:9</a> <em>It is not chained</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:12\">HEB 4:12</a> <em>It is living and active</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a> <em>It is living and enduring.</em></p>\n<h2>Comparisons of the word of God with everyday things</h2>\n<p>Food:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:12\">JOB 23:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:103\">PSA 119:103</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:16\">JER 15:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:8\">EZK 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:1\">EZK 3:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:2\">1PE 2:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a> <em>light</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:14\">JER 5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:9\">JER 20:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:29\">JER 23:29</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:29\">JER 23:29</a> <em>a hammer</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:12\">HEB 4:12</a> <em>a two-edged sword</em></p>\n<h2>The word of God has power</h2>\n<h3>It is active</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:11\">ISA 55:11</a></strong> <em>The Hebrew for “word” can also mean “action” or “deed”. This indicates that God's word is active.</em></p>\n<h3>It brings about creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:6\">PSA 33:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:5\">2PE 3:5</a></p>\n<h3>It governs and maintains the created order</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:18\">PSA 147:18</a></p>\n<h3>It gives life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:2-Isa55:3\">ISA 55:2–55:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:4\">LUK 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>It consecrates secular things</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:5\">1TI 4:5</a> <em>“the word of God and prayer” probably means “scriptural prayer”; i.e., on the basis of scriptural teaching the believer offers thanksgiving and prayer.</em></p>\n<h3>It restrains from evil</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:4\">PSA 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:11\">PSA 119:11</a></p>\n<h3>It heals and rescues</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:20\">PSA 107:20</a></p>\n<h3>It has power to save</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:21\">JAS 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a></p>\n<h3>It brings about the growth of the kingdom of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:23\">MAT 13:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:20\">MRK 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:15\">LUK 8:15</a></p>\n<h3>It builds up the saints</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:32\">ACT 20:32</a></p>",
